content.rendered:
Directed by Raj Kumar Gupta.

Written by Raj Kumar Gupta.

Cast Arjun Kapoor(Prabhat Kumar). Sudev Nair(Yusuf). Rajesh Sharma(Rajesh Singh). Alexander Prasanth(Pillai). Santilal Mukherjee(Shaumik Biswas) . Sonia Albizuri(Immigration Officer). Sanjay Bhatia(Home Minister). Jiban Bhattarai(ISI Man(Nepal)). Nikhil Dave(Narang- Nepal Indian High Commission Head). Sudhir S. Dayma(Mr. Talwar). Sandeep Dhabale(Dheeraj). Ankita Dubey(Javed’s wife). Ankita Dubey(Javed’s wife). Amit Jairath(ISI Senior Officer). Aasif Khan(BIttu). Shubham Kumar(Shadab). Resh Lamba(Maachis). Lalit Kumar Malla(Nepal Police inspector Dreams cops). Devendra Mishra(Javed). Gaurav Mishra(Amit). Mayank Kumar Mishra(Bansi). Sonali Sharmistha Mohanty(Bittu’s sister). Namit(ISI chief). Madhukar Narlwade(Uday). Rahaao(ISI Man). Navneet Ranga(ATS officer Mumbai). Shakti Rawal(Fareed). Jeetu Shastri(Friend (as Jeetendra Shastri)). Mohit Sheoran(Shadab Ali Farooqui). Bajrangbali Singh(Ravi). Pravin Singh Sisodia(Manish).Ammar Taalwala. Umesh Tamang(Nadeem). Vineeta Thakur(Prabhat’s wife). Divya Unny(Mrs. Iyer). Tyrone Aviet(Dancer in Dilbar Jani (uncredited))

Language Hindi.

Producers Prassanth Kumar Chandran. Vighnesh Chendwankar. Arun Doshi. Raj Kumar Gupta. Myra Karn. Sanjeevkumar Nair. Shyam Tallamraju. Shantanu Tungare.

Production Fox STAR Studios. Raapchik Films. Reverie Entertainment.
